
Description
    Output a bang for any interaction

Category
    Graphic

Arguments

Options

Inlet 0
    Anything - Trigger a bang out for any entry

Outlet 0
    Bang - Bang!

Details
    A graphical object that outputs a bang whenever it is clicked on with the mouse.
    It also converts anything it received in its inlet into a bang sent out its outlet.
    It highlights itself with a brief flash whenever it is triggered.
